CNCP v1 24052
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#13184: When dynamically updating the <ion-item> within the <ion-radio-group>, you encounter the error \"NotFoundError: Failed to execute 'insertBefore' on 'Node': The node before which the new node is to be inserted is not a child of this node.\"",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:21:01.831755+00:00",
  "text": "When dynamically updating the <ion-item> within the <ion-radio-group>, you encounter the error \"NotFoundError: Failed to execute 'insertBefore' on 'Node': The node before which the new node is to be inserted is not a child of this node.\"\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.13\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n等待5秒;\n然后就会报错: NotFoundError: Failed to execute 'insertBefore' on 'Node': The node before which the new node is to be inserted is not a child of this node.\n\n### What is expected?\n\n渲染新的数据\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\n移除的不会导致错误; \n增加会导致错误;\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n我在 ionic 提交了错误报告: https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30343#issuecomment-2790657415;\n那边分析说是 vue 渲染行为导致的该问题; 这是一个错误吗? \n只在  <script lang=\"ts\" steup> 下存在该问题;",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "need more info"
  ],
